| Concept             | Purpose                           | Keywords                       |
| ------------------- | --------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| SELECT              | Fetch data                        | SELECT                         |
| WHERE               | Filter rows                       | WHERE, AND, OR, IN, BETWEEN    |
| ORDER BY            | Sort data                         | ASC, DESC                      |
| DISTINCT            | Remove duplicates                 | DISTINCT                       |
| LIMIT/TOP           | Fetch top records                 | LIMIT, TOP                     |
| Aggregate Functions | Calculations                      | COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX      |
| GROUP BY            | Group data                        | Department-wise, Category-wise |
| HAVING              | Filter grouped data               | HAVING                         |
| CASE WHEN           | Conditional logic                 | CASE                           |
| Joins               | Combine tables                    | INNER, LEFT, RIGHT, FULL       |
| Self Join           | Same table join                   | SELF JOIN                      |
| Cross Join          | Cartesian product                 | CROSS JOIN                     |
| Subquery            | Query inside query                | Nested Query                   |
| Correlated Subquery | Row-by-row comparison             | EXISTS                         |
| CTE                 | Temporary result set              | WITH                           |
| Window Functions    | Ranking & analytics               | OVER()                         |
| ROW_NUMBER()        | Unique ranking                    | PARTITION BY                   |
| RANK()              | Ranking with gaps                 | RANK                           |
| DENSE_RANK()        | Ranking without gaps              | DENSE_RANK                     |
| LEAD()              | Next row value                    | LEAD                           |
| LAG()               | Previous row value                | LAG                            |
| UNION               | Combine results remove duplicates | UNION                          |
| UNION ALL           | Combine results keep duplicates   | UNION ALL                      |
| INTERSECT           | Common records                    | INTERSECT                      |
| EXCEPT              | Difference records                | EXCEPT                         |
| String Functions    | Text operations                   | UPPER, LOWER, SUBSTRING        |
| Date Functions      | Date operations                   | GETDATE, DATEADD, DATEDIFF     |
| NULL Handling       | Missing values                    | IS NULL, COALESCE              |
| Views               | Virtual table                     | CREATE VIEW                    |
| Stored Procedure    | Reusable SQL block                | CREATE PROCEDURE               |
| Functions (UDF)     | Custom logic                      | CREATE FUNCTION                |
| Triggers            | Auto execution                    | CREATE TRIGGER                 |
| Indexes             | Performance                       | CLUSTERED, NONCLUSTERED        |
| Transactions        | Data consistency                  | BEGIN, COMMIT, ROLLBACK        |
| Pivot               | Rows to columns                   | PIVOT                          |
| Unpivot             | Columns to rows                   | UNPIVOT                        |
| Merge               | UPSERT operation                  | MERGE                          |
| Dynamic SQL         | Runtime query creation            | EXEC                           |
